<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.logging.LogTargetFile.Create" Title="Create method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.LogTargetFile">LogTargetFile</PageRef> ->
    Create
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>Create</TypeRef> method creates a file target and returns it wrapped in a smart pointer compatible with <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.LogManager.AddLogTarget">LogManager.AddLogTarget</PageRef>.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[static std::unique_ptr<LogTargetFile, ILogTarget::Deleter> Create();]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="LogTargetFile!cobalt.logging.LogTargetFile">
        A newly constructed <TypeRef>LogTargetFile</TypeRef> object wrapped in a smart pointer that uses <TypeRef>ILogTarget::Deleter</TypeRef>.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="See also">
    <PageRefList>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.logging.LogTargetFile">LogTargetFile</PageRefListEntry>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.logging.LogManager.AddLogTarget">LogManager.AddLogTarget</PageRefListEntry>
    </PageRefList>
  </Section>
</XMLDocContent>
